      ],
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Slack ChatOps loop\nSlack Events API -> `/webhook/slack-chatops` -> parse command -> SSH to devbox-104 -> ansible-playbook -> result back to the originating channel.\n\n**Setup after import:**\n1. Create `devbox-104 SSH` credential (SSH private key \u2014 Credentials store, NOT Variables).\n2. Attach `Slack Bot (ops-agent)` credential to Slack nodes.\n3. On devbox-104: `echo <vault-pass> > ~/.vault_pass && chmod 600 ~/.vault_pass`.\n4. Activate, then point the Slack app Event Subscriptions at this webhook.",
        "width": 460,
        "height": 320
      }
    }
